 Hospital Insurance Claims Analysis

## Project Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes hospital insurance claim data to identify claim trends, approval rates, processing time, and business insights.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- SQL
- Microsoft Excel
- Power Query
- DAX

## Key Insights
- Claim approval trends
- Claim status analysis
- Department-wise claims
- Monthly claim analysis

